00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:35.760
nos comprometimos

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:38.080
a eliminar la renta vitalicia

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:41.520
mi persona a las dos semanas de asumir el el gobierno

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:42.760
